data.text:
The Oscar Schmidt OG2CE acoustic electric guitar is a deep dreadnought with a full acoustic resonance. This OG2CESM features a beautiful spalted maple top with high gloss natural finish, cutaway body, catalpa back and sides, rosewood fingerboard and bridge, and an easy action mahogany neck. Perfect for beginners and experienced players alike, this Oscar Schmidt OG2CESM offers playability and a great sound, complimented by the unique looks of the spalted maple top.
